react-tipsy Changelog
=====================

Here you can see the full list of changes between each react-tipsy release.

Version 0.4.0
-------------

Released on January 26, 2017.

- Library name chaned from "ReactTipsy" to "Tipsy"
- updated package.json to not be reliant on a specific React/ReactDOM versoin
- updated README.md to fix typos and include props options and methods
- added touch support (ontouchstart and ontouchend events)
- added "manual" trigger
- added new public methods: "toggle", "updatePosition" and "destroy"